				<td colspan="2"><span>Very few swarm spots give good loot, but at 51, you should be able to do any of the following swarm camps for great exp. (listed in order of less to more exp IMHO):  Check out other posts for details, there are TONS of them...
<br />

<br />
1) Raptors in TD
<br />
2) Toilers in ME
<br />
3) Flies and rats in PoD
<br />

<br />
The easier they are, the less exp and less resists you'll get.
<br />

<br />
GL and keep leveling and having fun!
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
